params.name: do_resize
params.description: Whether to resize the images (height, width) dimensions, rounding them down to the closest multiple ofsize_divisor. Can be overridden by do_resize in preprocess.

params.name: size_divisor
params.description: When do_resize is True, images are resized so their height and width are rounded down to the closestmultiple of size_divisor. Can be overridden by size_divisor in preprocess.

params.name: resample
params.description: Resampling filter to use if resizing the image. Can be overridden by resample in preprocess.

params.name: do_rescale
params.description: Whether or not to apply the scaling factor (to make pixel values floats between 0. and 1.). Can beoverridden by do_rescale in preprocess.
